lead_paragraph: Carl Icahn accused New Jersey's Senate president of "selling out" Atlantic City by considering casinos near New York City, while the legislative leader said the state wouldn't give the billionaire investor the tax breaks he is seeking.

headline.main: Icahn: Senate Leader 'Selling Out' Atlantic City
